commit.message: chores: fix version typo in CHANGES.md
fix: compare_digest actually appeared in python 2.7.7

fix: define a compatibility method for py2.6

compare_digest did only appear in python 2.7 and above
defining a way of compare two hashes with protections
against timing attacks.

We define the same function for lower versions of python
but without the time attacks protection.
